{
  "id": "adv_card_kan_07_01",
  "title": "kana 1話 こころのやつ、絶対泣かす",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_festivalstage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_07_01-kan001.m4a",
      "text": "やったね、こころちゃん！　kana達が優勝だよ！！\n当然だよね、だってkana達が一番仲いいし！！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We did it‚ Kokoro-chan! We won!!\nOf course! We're the closest friends‚ after all!!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 4.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_festivalstage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 9.5161900838
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_07_01-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "（kanaさんとこころのユニットはイベントで優勝）\n（見事、冠番組とCMの仕事を獲得した）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（Kana and Kokoro's unit won the event）\n（and successfully landed a flagship show and a commercial.）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 12.9666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_07_01-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "（最初は不安だったけど）\n（あの二人、本当に仲良くなれたんだな）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（I was worried at first‚ but）\n（those two really did become friends.）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 19.5333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――『星見フレンドフェス』終了後",
      "translations": {
        "en": "—After the \"Hoshimi Friend Fes\" ended",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 23.7725847244,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-01-noon",
      "startTime": 25.3659166336
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-01-noon",
      "startTime": 25.3659166336
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_07_01-kan002.m4a",
      "text": "あ～、やっと終わった",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ahh‚ it's finally over.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 26.2659142178,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_07_01-kan003.m4a",
      "text": "……ったく、収録で疲れてんのに\n今後のスケジュールとか、そんな話明日にしろっての",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Jeez‚ I'm tired from recording‚\ntell them to talk about future schedules tomorrow.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 31.8906482031,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-01-noon",
      "startTime": 36.5698597511
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_07_01-kan004.m4a",
      "text": "むふふふふ、でもkanaが優勝したもんね\nふふん、ますますkanaの知名度上がっちゃうな～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Muhahaha‚ but I won‚ didn't I?\nHehe‚ my recognition is going to increase even more~",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 41.2163932164,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-01-noon",
      "startTime": 45.5497235537
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_07_01-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "改めまして、優勝おめでとうございます\nそれにしても、こころと息バッチリでしたね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Congratulations on your victory once again.\nBut still‚ your timing with Kokoro was perfect.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 49.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-01-noon",
      "startTime": 53.1940090735
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_07_01-kan005.m4a",
      "text": "はん。あんなの演技よ、演技",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hmph. That was just acting‚ acting.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 53.1940090735,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_07_01-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "え！？\nさっきまで、あんなに気が合ってたのに",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Huh?!\nBut you two seemed to get along so well just now.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 57.4666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-01-noon",
      "startTime": 60.5711509227
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_07_01-kan006.m4a",
      "text": "スリクスのマネージャーになって結構経つのに\nあんた、kana達の何を見てたのよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It's been quite a while since you became the ⅢX manager.\nWhat have you been watching about us?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 63.7161426703,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_07_01-kan007.m4a",
      "text": "仲良しのフリは慣れてんの\nkanaがあんなガキと仲良くなる訳ないじゃん",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I'm used to pretending to be close.\nThere's no way I'd become close with a brat like that.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 68.9494760036,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-01-noon",
      "startTime": 72.3811280727
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_07_01-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "……説得力あり過ぎますね……\nで、でも、仲良しユニットってことで優勝したのに……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…That's a little too convincing…\nB-but‚ you won under the premise of being a close unit…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 75.3666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_07_01-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "冠番組が続く間はずっとこころと一緒ですし\nCMでは二人でアイスを半分こ、とかやるんですよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You'll be with Kokoro the entire time the flagship show lasts.\nAnd in the commercial‚ you two will be splitting an ice cream‚ right?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 83.6718567653,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_07_01-kan008.m4a",
      "text": "だ～いじょうぶだって",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It's fiiine.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 88.6975266934,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-01-noon",
      "startTime": 88.6975266934
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_07_01-kan009.m4a",
      "text": "あいつと違って、kanaは業界歴長いんだから\nカメラの前ではちゃんとやってやるから、安心しなよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Unlike that brat‚ I have a long career in the industry.\nI'll perform properly in front of the camera‚ so don't worry.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 95.4992079576,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-01-noon",
      "startTime": 99.0861208042
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_07_01-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "（kanaさんはスリクスで慣れてるだろうけど）\n（今回はどちらかと言えば、こころがなぁ）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（Kana-san is probably used to it from ⅢX‚）\n（but this time‚ if anything‚ I'm worried about Kokoro.）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 102,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_07_01-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "（こころがkanaさんをスルー出来るとは思えないし）\n（長丁場の仕事の間に何が起こるか……いや、やらかすか）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（I doubt Kokoro can ignore Kana-san‚）\n（What might happen during a long-term job… or rather‚ what mess will she make?）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 109.9333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――冠番組の初回収録後",
      "translations": {
        "en": "—After the first recording of the flagship show",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 116.5874786139,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 118.0874795038
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 118.0874795038
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_07_01-kan010.m4a",
      "text": "くっそ、あのガキ！！\n最初だから、こっちは気合い入れてたのに",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Damn that brat!!\nIt was the first time‚ so I was all fired up.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 120.9672309081,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 123.9280670881
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_07_01-kan011.m4a",
      "text": "いきなりシュークリームにワサビ入れる\nドッキリ仕掛けてくるとか！！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "To suddenly pull a prank like\nputting wasabi in a cream puff!!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 126.0338975747,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_07_01-kan012.m4a",
      "text": "テレビ映り悪くなるから、吹き出さないようにするの\nどれだけ大変だったか、あいつ分かってんのか！！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I tried not to spit it out so I wouldn't look bad on TV.\nDoes that brat even realize how tough that was!!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 131.1672309081,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 135.071332844
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_07_01-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "（あああ、また殴る用のぬいぐるみが尊い犠牲に……）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（Aargh‚ another punching plushie has become a noble sacrifice…）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 135.071332844,
      "sfxList": [
