        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_pillow-01.m4a",
          "delay": 2895.333822699996,
          "startTime": 137.9666666667
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 140.5199722369
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_07_01-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "こ……こころが番組スタッフに提案してたみたいですね\nkanaさんのドッキリのリアクション芸は鉄板だって",
      "translations": {
        "en": "K-Kokoro seems to have suggested it to the show staff.\nThat Kana-san's prank reactions are guaranteed hits.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 144.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 148.3189496119
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_07_01-kan013.m4a",
      "text": "どっかの映画監督みたいなこと言いやがって！\nやりたくてドッキリに出てる訳じゃないっつーの！",
      "translations": {
